==製作==
2014年4月10日，[[西恩·潘|西恩·潘]]將於戰區題材的劇情片《''The Last Face''》中擔任導演，而[[莎莉·賽隆|莎莉·賽隆]]和[[哈維爾·巴登|哈維爾·巴登]]將作為主演<ref>{{cite web |last=Busch |first=Anita |url=http://deadline.com/2014/04/last-face-movie-sean-penn-charlize-theron-javier-bardem-africa-712605/ |title=Sean Penn To Direct Charlize Theron and Javier Bardem In ‘The Last Face’ |publisher=Deadline |date=2014-04-10 |accessdate=2016-05-06 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116054432/https://deadline.com/2014/04/last-face-movie-sean-penn-charlize-theron-javier-bardem-africa-712605/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主要攝影於2014年8月1日在[[開普敦|開普敦]]開始進行<ref>{{cite web |last=Thomas |first=Kate |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2713198/Charlize-Theron-Javier-Bardem-kick-filming-romantic-drama-The-Last-Face-Cape-Town.html |title=Charlize Theron and Javier Bardem kick off filming for The Last Face in Cape Town |publisher=Dailymail.co.uk |date=2014-08-01 |accessdate=2016-05-06 |archive-date=2016-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427135254/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2713198/Charlize-Theron-Javier-Bardem-kick-filming-romantic-drama-The-Last-Face-Cape-Town.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-81114-jurassic-world-wraps-the-last-face-starts/ |title=On The Set For 8/11/14: ‘Jurassic World’ Wraps, ‘The Last Face’ Starts |publisher=SSN Insider |date=2014-08-11 |accessdate=2016-05-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021035834/http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-81114-jurassic-world-wraps-the-last-face-starts/ |archivedate=2014-10-21 }}</ref>。

==發行==
[[File:Cannes_2016_40.jpg|thumb]]
《戰地情》於2016年5月20日在[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]上首映<ref>{{cite web |author=Owen Gleiberman |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-the-last-face-sean-penn-charlize-theron-1201779501/ |title=Cannes review: Charlize Theron in Sean Penn’s The Last Face’ |publisher=Variety |date=2016-05-20 |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2018-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619085947/https://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-the-last-face-sean-penn-charlize-theron-1201779501/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不久後，{{link-en|薩班資本集團|Saban Capital Group|薩班影業}}收購了該片的美國發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/saban-films-sean-penns-the-last-face-release-date-1201815533/|title=Saban Films To Distribute Sean Penn’s ‘The Last Face’|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Anita|last=Busch|date=September 8, 2016|accessdate=September 8, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126133346/https://deadline.com/2016/09/saban-films-sean-penns-the-last-face-release-date-1201815533/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

